extendedInfo.description: Face Tagger is a simpler and more convenient way to tag your Facebook photos. By integrating face recognition technology, Face Tagger's "Auto Tag" feature allows it to recognize your Facebook friend's faces and offer to automatically tag them on facebook. Face Tagger is designed to be a "download-once app". Meaning, if you have external storage on your phone, the albums and photos you view will be saved on your external card for easy and quick access the next time you view them.Features:â¢Â Simple and easy way to tag Facebook Photosâ¢ View Facebook Photo tagsâ¢ âAuto Tagâ feature that utilizes Face.comâs face recognition technology will assist you in automatically tagging your Facebook Friend's in your photosâ¢ View you and/or your Facebook friendâs photo albumsâ¢ View current Facebook photo tags and set new tagsâ¢ Upload photos to Facebook albumsâ¢ Train you and/or your friendâs face for better facial detectionâ¢ View face recognition details including: age, gender, smiling, glasses, etc.â¢ External storage used to store downloaded albums and photos for quick and easy access.Request a feature!If you have any force closes,problems,questions, or feature requests, feel free to contact the developer at: TheProdigy090@gmail.comI would like to work with you to solve any force closes or problems you may have with the app.Keywords: Facebook Photo Tagging, Facebook Tag Photos, Set FB Tags, Face Recognition, Tag Facebook Photos, Age detection, tag photo, Face Detection, Age detection, Detect your age, Guess your age
